data.description: *UNDER CONTRACT. SELLER ACCEPTING BACK UP OFFERS* The most perfect location for your new home by the beach -- welcome to 120 Mosaic Oaks Circle! This home is conveniently located only ten minutes to the nearest beach access, grocery stores, shopping, dining, schools and so much more. Prefer the bay to the beach? That's nearby too! Mosaic Oaks is a quiet and safe community centrally located to the countless amenities in South Walton. This three bedroom, two and a half bathroom home has been extremely well cared for and lovingly maintained. The main level offers a generously sized, wrap around covered porch, upgraded kitchen, two dining spaces,  spacious family room and half bathroom. Upstairs you will find the oversized primary suite, two guest rooms and guest bath as well. This home is filled with endless amounts of natural light and charm -- come by and take a look! Contact your agent to schedule a private viewing today!
